    • thrownStore

      public MethodExecStore.Builder thrownStore​(ThrownStore value)
      Specifies the store to use for gathering statistics on thrown exceptions.

      Can be used to capture thrown exception stats across multiple MethodExecStore objects.

      If not specified, one will be created by default for the MethodExecStore object.

      Parameters:
      value - The store to use for gathering statistics on thrown exceptions.

      This object.
